Index: drivers/net/wireless/hostap_ap.c
--- drivers/net/wireless/hostap_ap.c.orig	2003-08-12 14:39:16.000000000 -0400
+++ drivers/net/wireless/hostap_ap.c	2003-06-23 18:52:56.000000000 -0400
