Index: drivers/net/wireless/hostap_hw.c
--- drivers/net/wireless/hostap_hw.c.orig	2003-08-12 14:39:16.000000000 -0400
+++ drivers/net/wireless/hostap_hw.c	2003-08-08 22:39:41.000000000 -0400
